            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-lg-12">
                	<h2>What is Future Blue?</h2>
                	<p>
                		Future Blue is the intern networking and social community that is operated by IBM's Campus Recruitment team. It operates four distinct teams that focus on different aspects of intern life at IBM: Social Events, Career &amp; Development, Communications, and Web.
                	</p>
                	<h2>What is the Web Team?</h2>
                	<p>
                		The Future Blue Web Team is the intern community at IBM. Our main goal is to learn new &amp; cool technologies by using them.
                	</p>
                	<p>
						We want to help improve the IBM community by building all sorts of apps that IBMers could benefit from. Currently, our team uses Bluemix, Node.js, Ruby on Rails, and more. We believe that IBM at heart is a tech company, and we take pride in creating innovative applications by using the latest practices and technology.
                	</p>
                </div>
