						<h3>Future Blue Internal Web Page</h3>
					</a>
					<p class="margin-top">
						Future Blue's <a href="/" class="highlight">Internal Web Page</a> is the Web Team's official home, available within the IBM intranet at <a href="http://futureblue.torolab.ibm.com" class="highlight">futureblue.torolab.ibm.com</a>. It showcases what the web team's all about, and features a suggestion box for any IBMer to suggest project ideas. It's built using <a href="https://nodejs.org/" class="highlight">Node.js</a> and the <a href="https://expressjs.com/" class="highlight">Express.js</a> framework.
					</p>
					<p>
